column5: I just had to reach out and say thanks to the angler I was fishing with today in the Shawa providing me with tips and ROE!  I'll have to drop Rudy a note to say thanks to you too just incase you miss this.  THANKS AGAIN and I hope we cross paths again...  Cheers and THANKS! Geoff
ha ha ...ill accept it on his behalf....j/k....but true fishermen are the best guys ever ...
tks twocoda, I'll msg Manning too...    CHEERS!
Fishin in the shwa eh?  It was blown pretty bad today, but i expect it to be fishable tomorrow.  Ill be out most of the afternoon, fishin oshawa if you want to join me
tks kemper, I'm heading to Barrie in an hour for a few days otherwise I would join ya for sure!
